01:27:45.135 --> 01:27:49.049
a commitment to something that is bigger
than myself

01:27:49.556 --> 01:27:53.220
and, I can't break that to just...

01:27:56.104 --> 01:27:59.313
- ease my mind. Or my fears. My...
- love

01:28:07.699 --> 01:28:09.281
I just wanted to say I'm sorry.

01:28:13.288 --> 01:28:14.199
And I'm back.

01:28:17.417 --> 01:28:18.373
God bless.

01:28:20.545 --> 01:28:21.456
God bless.

01:28:26.176 --> 01:28:27.132
Before you go,

01:28:29.679 --> 01:28:30.669
think I could run

01:28:31.765 --> 01:28:33.256
part of my homily by you?

01:28:33.683 --> 01:28:34.764
You want my feedback?

01:28:38.396 --> 01:28:39.307
Okay.

01:28:39.898 --> 01:28:42.436
Have you been reading much, John lately?

01:28:43.193 --> 01:28:48.359
Yeah. Well, I'm a little bit more of a
Ringo man myself. But...

01:28:50.951 --> 01:28:53.364
- Sorry.
- Laugh pause.

01:28:54.788 --> 01:28:57.201
That actually was pretty funny.

01:28:59.501 --> 01:29:00.412
Trust yourself.

01:29:05.632 --> 01:29:08.124
No one has ever seen God.

01:29:10.345 --> 01:29:12.803
But, if we love each other,

01:29:14.182 --> 01:29:15.718
God lives in us.

01:29:17.686 --> 01:29:18.597
John

01:29:19.312 --> 01:29:20.223
4-12.

01:29:21.314 --> 01:29:24.853
I probably read that over 100 times
in my life.

01:29:25.235 --> 01:29:26.601
I thought I knew what it meant

01:29:27.487 --> 01:29:30.230
but it turns out I never really understood

01:29:31.616 --> 01:29:32.732
much about it at all.

01:29:34.786 --> 01:29:36.527
Seeing God.

01:29:37.581 --> 01:29:40.039
It's not that I don't see him.

01:29:41.334 --> 01:29:42.245
I do.

01:29:43.420 --> 01:29:47.084
It's just that I've always assumed
that it could be done only one way,

01:29:49.009 --> 01:29:50.716
through prayer,

01:29:51.219 --> 01:29:52.175
through faith,

01:29:52.512 --> 01:29:55.471
through the perfect ritual of mass.

01:29:56.474 --> 01:29:57.590
If it worked for me,

01:29:58.435 --> 01:29:59.767
why not everyone else?

01:30:03.940 --> 01:30:06.182
If we love each other,

01:30:08.028 --> 01:30:09.564
God lives in us.

01:30:11.364 --> 01:30:13.105
What does that really mean?

01:30:14.618 --> 01:30:17.406
love itself cannot be defined or...

01:30:19.414 --> 01:30:20.450
understood, or...

01:30:20.832 --> 01:30:21.993
Quantified...

01:30:23.710 --> 01:30:24.621
denied.

01:30:28.340 --> 01:30:31.378
If God is a mystery,

01:30:32.385 --> 01:30:34.251
love probably is as well.

01:30:36.431 --> 01:30:38.423
Because, at the end of the day,

01:30:39.684 --> 01:30:42.643
after a lifetime of theological study,

01:30:44.230 --> 01:30:47.064
my knowledge of love and God

01:30:48.068 --> 01:30:52.233
amounts to little more
than these two truths:

01:30:54.491 --> 01:30:55.402
One:

01:30:56.493 --> 01:30:57.734
they both exist.

01:30:59.120 --> 01:31:00.156
And two:

01:31:01.164 --> 01:31:05.158
when it comes to the matters of God
and the matters of love,

01:31:08.254 --> 01:31:10.246
I can no longer tell the difference.

01:31:12.884 --> 01:31:14.091
And for this,

01:31:16.179 --> 01:31:17.511
I feel blessed.

